{"type": "article", "id": 14651, "title": "Nike Air Max 1 OG", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-09T07:27:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000316DZ0hcHVNxgr6nCQp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自香港的设计师 Ben Darmon，根据耐克 1987 年推出的 Nike Air Max 1 系列红白款 ，制作了一盏霓虹光管 Nike Air Max 1 OG。红白相间的灯管勾勒出鞋子的外形，具有极高的辨识度。187 盏限量，也是为了纪念它出产的年代。有趣的是，它使用了鞋盒做包装，让购买的人感受到不仅仅是买鞋子，还有永恒的经典。售价 199 欧，<a href=\"http://sneakerdeco.com/home/8-table-top-neon-lamp-air-max-1-og-red-limited-edition.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142116EaWkeG5r8BY0XIvc.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142117DEP6TYktOBU2hWoN.jpg\" width=\"872\" height=\"582\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66743119\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142117zT3lN2KGLrDyOxiC.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"463\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142118WB7RwTzy9xYdHsL6.jpg\" width=\"676\" height=\"731\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.08136095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}